                    "locale": {
                        "el-gr": {
                            "display_title": "Το Υπνοδωμάτιο της Μία",
                            "description": "Η Μία μαθαίνει να παίζει ντραμς και εξασκείται με τα δικά της ντραμς στο υπνοδωμάτιό της. Δυνάμωσε το ραδιόφωνο και κράτα το ρυθμό των αγαπημένων της τραγουδιών! Μετά, ξάπλωσε στο κρεβάτι της και γράψε κάτι στο ημερολόγιό της. Φύλαξε το ημερολόγιο της Μία στο κομοδίνο της και κρύψε μαζί και τα γράμματά της! Περιλαμβάνει μίνι φιγούρα της Μία.",
                            "title": "Το Υπνοδωμάτιο της Μία",
                            "tags": []
                        },
                        "en-us": {
                            "bullet_points": "•  Includes Mia mini-doll figure\r\n•  Features table, bed and drum set\r\n•  Accessories include radio, vase, table, lamp, diary and basket\r\n•  Store Mia's diary in the bedside table!\r\n•  Hide a special letter inside of Mia's diary or in the drawer!\r\n•  Rock out on the drums to Mia's favorite radio songs!\r\n•  LEGO® Friends pieces are fully compatible with all LEGO System bricks\r\n•  Collect all of the LEGO Friends sets for a whole city of LEGO Friends fun!\r\n•  LEGO mini-dolls are figures made especially forthe world of LEGO Friends, with thousands of customizable fashion and accessory combinations!\r\n•  Bed measures over 2” (6cm) tall, 2” (6cm) wide and 2” (6cm) long\r\n•  Drum set measures over 1” (3cm) tall, 1” (4cm) wide and 1” (4cm) long",
                            "display_title": "Mia’s Bedroom",
                            "one_liner": "Crank up the radio in Mia's Bedroom with a a drum set, bed and table, then write in her diary while keeping the beat to her favorite songs!",
                            "description": "Mia is learning to play the drums and practices on her very own drum set in her bedroom. Crank up the radio and keep the beat to her favorite songs! Then stretch out on her bed and write in her diary. Keep Mia's diary tucked safely away in her bedside table and hide her letters inside! Includes Mia mini-doll figure.",
